"""Test get_resource."""
message = self.common.get_resource(self.data.array, 'sloprovisioning',
    'volume', resource_name=None, params=None)
self.assertEqual(self.data.volume_list[2], message)
message_1 = self.common.get_resource(category='sloprovisioning',
    resource_level='symmetrix', resource_level_id=self.data.array,
    resource_type='volume')
self.assertEqual(self.data.volume_list[2], message_1)
